name: web-project-template
description: This is a web project template.

scripts.命令说明: 为什么没直接用“webpack”作为命令呢！而是用“./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack.js”呢！是因为，使用后者的方式可以在启用node的各个选项的同时运行“webpack”，比如启用node的某些实验性选项以使node在运行webpack的配置文件时支持配置文件使用某些ECMAScript的提案语法书写配置文件。
scripts.dev: node --experimental-import-meta-resolve --experimental-network-imports --experimental-shadow-realm --experimental-vm-modules --experimental-wasm-modules --experimental-websocket --max-http-header-size=1024000 --no-warnings --no-deprecation ./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack.js serve --color --profile --mode development --env platform=dev_server --define-process-env-node-env development --config webpack.dev.esm.mjs
scripts.dashboard:dev: node --experimental-import-meta-resolve --experimental-network-imports --experimental-shadow-realm --experimental-vm-modules --experimental-wasm-modules --experimental-websocket --max-http-header-size=1024000 --no-warnings --no-deprecation ./node_modules/webpack-dashboard/bin/webpack-dashboard.js --title 仪表板模式 -- node --experimental-import-meta-resolve --experimental-network-imports --experimental-shadow-realm --experimental-vm-modules --experimental-wasm-modules --experimental-websocket --max-http-header-size=1024000 --no-warnings --no-deprecation ./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack.js serve --color --profile --mode development --env platform=dev_server --define-process-env-node-env development --config webpack.dev.esm.mjs
scripts.nodemon:dev: nodemon --ext json,json5,js,cjs,mjs,ts,cts,mts,crt,key,pem,p12 --ignore configures/update_graphQL_schema_json --ignore configures/update_tsconfig_lib --watch configures --watch webpack.dev.esm.mjs --watch postcss.config.mjs --watch postcss.postcss-modules.config.mjs --watch tsconfig.webpack.json --watch webpack.base.esm.mjs --exec npm run dev
